content: Premium rates with GST for aged fifty one and above for twenty six months policy are one thousand four hundred four dollars and seventy cents for Basic plan, one thousand four hundred sixty nine dollars and thirty cents for Enhanced plan, one thousand five hundred one dollars and ninety cents for Premier plan, and one thousand six hundred ten dollars and thirty cents for Exclusive plan.
